OL,3,CHay fever sufferers warned as UK set
OL,4,Cto see hottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FA notable burst of early summer warmth
OL,7,Fis building across the UK, with very
OL,8,Fhigh temperatures and long spells of
OL,9,Fsunshine over the next few days.
OL,11,FToday (Tuesday) and Wednesday will
OL,12,Fbring the hottest weather of the year
OL,13,Fso far, with temperatures widely
OL,14,Freaching the low twenties and peaking
OL,15,Fat 26C in parts of south-east England.
OL,17,FWarmest day of the year so far
OL,19,FToday's temperatures are well above
OL,20,Faverage for early April.
