OL,3,CHay fever sufferers warned as UK set
OL,4,Cto see hottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FMany areas will reach 22C - 23C,
OL,7,Fmaking it the warmest day of the year
OL,8,Fso far.
OL,10,FIt is likely to surpass the current
OL,11,Fhighest recorded temperature of 2026,
OL,12,Fwhich was 20.9C in Pershore,
OL,13,FWorcestershire, on March 31.
OL,15,FIt also looks set to be the warmest
OL,16,Fearly April spell since 2020, when
OL,17,F26C was recorded at Treknow in
OL,18,FCornwall on April 10.
