OL,3,CHay fever sufferers warned as UK set
OL,4,Cto see hottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FBy Wednesday, the warmth builds
OL,7,Ffurther, with the Midlands, East
OL,8,FAnglia and south-east England seeing
OL,9,Fthe highest temperatures, potentially
OL,10,Freaching 24C to 26C.
OL,12,FSunny and very warm for most
OL,14,FFor the majority, it will be dry,
OL,15,Fsunny and very warm.
OL,17,FA south to south-easterly breeze is
OL,18,Fdrawing in warmer air from the near
OL,19,Fcontinent.
