OL,3,CHay fever sufferers warned as UK set
OL,4,Cto see hottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FWith lighter winds and strong
OL,7,Fsunshine, it will feel more like
OL,8,Fsummer than spring.
OL,10,FThere will be a little more cloud at
OL,11,Ftimes across Scotland and Northern
OL,12,FIreland, with the chance of an
OL,13,Fisolated shower, but even here it will
OL,14,Fstill feel mild.
OL,16,FHigh pollen levels
OL,18,FWith the increased sunshine and rising
OL,19,Ftemperatures, pollen levels are also
OL,20,Fclimbing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
