OL,3,CHay fever sufferers warned as UK set
OL,4,Cto see hottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FLevels will be high across England and
OL,7,FWales, and in parts of Scotland,
OL,8,Fparticularly for tree pollen. Birch
OL,9,Fpollen is a key trigger at this time
OL,10,Fof year.
OL,12,FFor many hay fever sufferers, their
OL,13,Fsymptoms may be more noticeable in the
OL,14,Fcoming days.
OL,16,FTree pollen season typically runs from
OL,17,FMarch through to early June.
OL,19,FWarmth holding on in the South-East
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
