OL,3,CHay fever sufferers warned as UK set
OL,4,Cto see hottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FWhile a change begins to edge in from
OL,7,Fthe west on Thursday, the South-East
OL,8,Fis likely to hold on to the warmest
OL,9,Fconditions, with temperatures still
OL,10,Freaching around 20C.
OL,12,FA change later in the week
OL,14,FThe warmer air will gradually be
OL,15,Freplaced by something cooler as we
OL,16,Fmove through Thursday and into the end
OL,17,Fof the week.
OL,19,FTemperatures are expected to ease back
OL,20,Fcloser to average, and more changeable
OL,21,Fconditions will be developing.
